1
00:00:14,940 --> 00:00:16,180
♪The spring breeze whispers
through the evening glow♪

2
00:00:16,780 --> 00:00:18,180
♪Wandering clouds ride a white steed♪

3
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:20,980
♪Plucking the stars from the sky♪

4
00:00:21,180 --> 00:00:23,140
♪Weaving them into a crown of blossoms♪

5
00:00:23,340 --> 00:00:25,100
♪Red hues tint both cheeks♪

6
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:27,340
♪A light boat glides through
the Milky Way♪

7
00:00:27,660 --> 00:00:30,500
♪Whose beautiful lass is laughing
on the Magpie Bridge?♪

8
00:00:31,980 --> 00:00:33,580
♪It's her♪

9
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Eager to see the world's splendor♪

10
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:38,100
♪Running down into the changing world♪

11
00:00:38,740 --> 00:00:40,380
♪A playful, innocent little lass♪

12
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:42,460
♪This bustling world♪

13
00:00:43,140 --> 00:00:44,780
♪As bright as a painting♪

14
00:00:45,380 --> 00:00:47,660
♪Look at how the fireworks
dye the spring breeze♪

15
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,460
♪The light breeze
stirs countless flowers♪

16
00:00:53,980 --> 00:00:56,860
♪Who smiles warmly among the leaves?♪

17
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:02,060
♪Let the years pass
with laughter and tears♪

18
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:04,220
♪In this world, let me♪

19
00:01:04,780 --> 00:01:06,020
♪Love♪

20
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:08,060
♪Freely♪

21
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:13,060
[When Fate Plays Matchmaker]

22
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:14,580
[Episode 2]

23
00:01:16,220 --> 00:01:18,420
Cheng,

24
00:01:18,420 --> 00:01:20,100
I'm at fault.

25
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:23,700
But before this,
I really didn't want to get married.

26
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:26,300
That's why I joined the Unfeeling Sect.

27
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:30,460
Now that she has appeared,

28
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:32,940
how can I let her go?

29
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:37,860
Do you forget how Senior died?

30
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:41,340
It's different.

31
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:43,380
Please just stay out of this.

32
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:49,420
If you divorce later on,

33
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:51,780
your child will suffer
for the rest of his life!

34
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:54,220
We're different from your parents...

35
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,460
Cheng,

36
00:02:02,460 --> 00:02:04,140
just let me do this.

37
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:05,700
I'm begging you,

38
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:06,500
Cheng.

39
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:08,340
I promise

40
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:11,180
that I will donate a large sum of money
to the sect every year

41
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:13,740
and serve Master well
until his last day.

42
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:17,900
I'll also get someone to serve you well.

43
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:19,980
Once I'm married,

44
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:22,340
I'll come back to let you go

45
00:02:22,340 --> 00:02:25,780
and get someone to escort you
back to the sect.

46
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:26,580
I'm going now.

47
00:02:27,740 --> 00:02:29,380
Li, listen to me!

48
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:34,060
This traitor.

49
00:02:34,740 --> 00:02:35,740
Watch him properly.

50
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:37,620
Don't let him come out.

51
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:38,860
Yes.

52
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:46,220
Get him!

53
00:02:46,220 --> 00:02:47,500
He's over there!

54
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:01,500
Senior!

55
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:06,380
Senior!

56
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,220
Don't fall in love

57
00:03:09,220 --> 00:03:13,020
or get married.

58
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:13,860
Senior.

59
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:15,860
Senior!

60
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:18,820
Senior!

61
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:23,300
Senior, don't worry.

62
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,940
I will stop Li from getting married.

63
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:28,370
[Bliss]

64
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:37,720
[Bride's Escort]

65
00:03:56,060 --> 00:03:57,300
So many?

66
00:03:58,180 --> 00:03:58,860
Marrying them all?

67
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,820
No way.

68
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:02,220
I'm only marrying Yurou.

69
00:04:08,860 --> 00:04:10,260
Cheng?

70
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:11,820
You...

71
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:13,170
What are you doing?

72
00:04:13,170 --> 00:04:14,220
Nothing.

73
00:04:15,780 --> 00:04:17,140
It's Mr. An

74
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:18,740
who asked me to test your sincerity.

75
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:20,860
If you can't pass this test,

76
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:23,820
this wedding is not happening.

77
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:26,180
Isn't he your assistant?

78
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,700
Why are you addressing him
like a friend?

79
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:30,860
Honestly, he's my friend.

80
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,180
There was a situation that day.

81
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:36,220
Whose side are you on?

82
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:39,820
I'm always on the side of reason.

83
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:42,900
Enough, let's not waste time.

84
00:04:42,900 --> 00:04:44,380
Otherwise, you'll miss
the auspicious time.

85
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,940
It's alright.
In my former practice with Yurou,

86
00:04:47,180 --> 00:04:48,140
I learned a few moves.

87
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:48,980
Don't worry.

88
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:49,980
Be careful.

89
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:55,860
Come on!

90
00:05:15,260 --> 00:05:18,500
The first question.
If your mother and wife

91
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:19,900
fall into the water in the meantime,

92
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:21,620
and you can only save one person,

93
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,300
who will you save?

94
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:24,700
The second question!

95
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,900
If after marriage, Miss An

96
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,540
still wants to explore the world

97
00:05:28,540 --> 00:05:29,780
and uphold justice,

98
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:31,860
how will you handle this as her husband?

99
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,700
What are your thoughts

100
00:05:34,700 --> 00:05:36,460
on having a daughter?

101
00:05:36,820 --> 00:05:37,820
If Miss An cannot bear a son,

102
00:05:37,820 --> 00:05:38,940
will the Li family
call this marriage off?

103
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:41,740
Can you live separately
from the Li family

104
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:42,940
after marriage?

105
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:45,940
Speak.

106
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:53,700
Cheng, there are so many people here.

107
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,460
Can you spare me?

108
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:58,100
There's nothing I can do.

109
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,380
How could I spare you?

110
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:00,540
These are

111
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:03,380
questions that Miss An wants answered.

112
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:04,260
So,

113
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:05,420
my hands are tied.

114
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,900
This person is interesting.

115
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,620
You dare to get in my way?

116
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:13,300
Today,

117
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:15,340
I'm here to help Miss An.

118
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:22,100
What should I do?

119
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,740
Shuangshuang, think of something.

120
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:30,900
Didn't you bring all your assets?

121
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:32,740
Give them all to Miss An.

122
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:34,300
That way she'll feel secure.

123
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:36,020
It will work.

124
00:06:45,980 --> 00:06:47,220
- Today...
- Music!

125
00:06:47,220 --> 00:06:49,620
I have something for you.

126
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:52,100
This is my seal and all my assets.

127
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:54,060
From today,

128
00:06:54,060 --> 00:06:55,100
everything I own

129
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:56,380
- You copycat!
- will belong to you.

130
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:57,940
So what if I copied you?

131
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,300
Since I first saw you,

132
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:02,180
I felt you were just and brave.

133
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:05,540
You're a heroine
who will uphold justice.

134
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:09,300
I know you long for a vast world

135
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:12,060
and hope to help the poor and weak.

136
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:14,580
I won't hold you back.

137
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:18,460
I, Li Jianshen, swear
by the Heavens and Earth

138
00:07:18,780 --> 00:07:19,900
that in this life,

139
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:21,900
I will be with you.

140
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:23,100
If I break this vow,

141
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,500
I will be cursed forever.

142
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:25,140
- Well said!
- Bravo!

143
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:31,900
What are you waiting for?

144
00:07:32,260 --> 00:07:33,260
Hurry and help me into the palanquin.

145
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:35,140
Miss An.

146
00:07:35,140 --> 00:07:37,940
Let the groom lift his bride
into the sedan chair!

147
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:43,060
You've left me with no choice.

148
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:52,620
Mr. Li, hurry up.

149
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:53,940
I...

150
00:07:53,940 --> 00:07:55,340
My legs won't budge.

151
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:58,540
Why is the palanquin just waiting there?

152
00:07:58,540 --> 00:07:59,740
Bring it in!

153
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:10,700
Why is it so hard to get married?

154
00:08:10,700 --> 00:08:12,180
Could it be

155
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:13,500
that the Heavens felt

156
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,300
this was not a good union?

157
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:17,540
Cheng,

158
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:19,180
- let me be!
- He is causing trouble again.

159
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:20,220
Why are you doing this to me?

160
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,620
What did I do?

161
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:23,420
Miss Zhao,

162
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:25,100
come here.

163
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,660
He's afraid of women.

164
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:27,860
If you flirt with him,
I'll be able to go.

165
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:38,340
Miss Zhao, hang in there!

166
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:56,180
♪Petals fall like rain
outside the window♪

167
00:08:57,180 --> 00:09:03,860
♪Murmurings whisper around my ears♪

168
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:11,620
♪My mind is clear at this moment♪

169
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:18,700
♪With a smile, the spring breeze
charms the years of youth♪

170
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:22,540
♪Affection's threads entwine♪

171
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:26,020
♪The journey stretches on and on♪

172
00:09:27,460 --> 00:09:34,060
♪My heart blooms with joy before you♪

173
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:38,140
♪Revealing what's hidden♪

174
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:40,900
♪Just in time for an old friend♪

175
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:47,900
♪Whose youth lingers,
awaiting my return?♪

176
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:53,500
♪With adoration, I trace your face♪

177
00:09:53,820 --> 00:09:56,980
♪The red candle sways,
my heart in disarray♪

178
00:09:57,340 --> 00:10:01,180
♪Who paints their longing
across their brow?♪

179
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:04,780
♪A hint of yearning gently swings♪

180
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:08,660
♪With love's brush, I trace your face♪

181
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:12,260
♪The red candle sways,
my heart in disarray♪

182
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:16,220
♪In shades of gray,
fate takes many turns♪

183
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:21,380
♪Unfolding my hand,
where fate's tale is etched♪
